      "IsMRef": true,
      "Title": "MonoCloud.Backend.Shared.ClientAuth.TlsAuth",
      "Summary": "<p sourcefile=\"api/MonoCloud.Backend.Shared.ClientAuth.TlsAuth.yml\" sourcestartlinenumber=\"1\">Provides TLS-based authentication for client applications using mutual TLS (mTLS).\nThis class implements the <xref href=\"MonoCloud.Backend.Shared.ClientAuth.IMonoCloudClientAuth\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref> interface.</p>\n<p>\nAuthentication is performed using an optional X509 certificate. If a certificate is not\nspecified, it is expected that the <xref href=\"MonoCloud.Backend.MonoCloudAuthenticationOptions.HttpClient\" data-throw-if-not-resolved=\"false\"></xref>\nis configured with a message handler that provides the client certificate.\n</p>\n<p>\nOptionally, a trust store id can be provided. If a trust store id is specified,\nthe corresponding trust store will be used to validate the server certificate.\nIf a trust store id is not specified, the default trust store will be used.\n</p>\n"
    },
